    }
    <div class="version-tag" @onclick="() => showChangelog = true">v1.5</div>

    @if (showChangelog)
    {
        <div class="changelog-overlay" @onclick="() => showChangelog = false">
            <div class="changelog-modal" @onclick:stopPropagation="true">
                <div class="changelog-header">
                    <span>📋 Changelog</span>
                    <button class="changelog-close" @onclick="() => showChangelog = false">✕</button>
                </div>
                <div class="changelog-body">

                    <div class="changelog-version">v1.5</div>
                    <ul class="changelog-list">
                        <li class="cl-new">Ability Setup page - manually assign turn and phase per ability before entering the roster view</li>
                        <li class="cl-new">Per-ability checkboxes: My Turn, Enemy Turn, Cmd, Mov, Sht, Chg, Fgt</li>
                        <li class="cl-new">Ability configs auto-populated from parsed phase data and saved to localStorage</li>
                        <li class="cl-new">Abilities button in footer to re-open setup at any time</li>
                        <li class="cl-new">Always active section for abilities with 4+ phases checked (exempt from phase filter)</li>
                        <li class="cl-new">Ability descriptions always visible on each item (no click needed)</li>
                        <li class="cl-changed">Ability panel items are now individual bordered cards - same visual style as stratagems</li>
                        <li class="cl-changed">Ability click-to-zoom matches stratagem zoom (blue border, left-strip, larger text)</li>
                        <li class="cl-changed">Show all now bypasses all filters (turn + phase + stat-reflected), was stat-reflected only</li>
                        <li class="cl-changed">Show all button renamed to Filter while active</li>
                        <li class="cl-changed">Phase and turn filtering for abilities driven by manual config</li>
                        <li class="cl-removed">Heuristic-based automatic turn detection for abilities</li>
                        <li class="cl-removed">Heuristic-based automatic phase detection for abilities</li>
