                    <div class="changelog-version">v1.1</div>
                    <ul class="changelog-list">
                        <li class="cl-new">Stratagems panel - Core and Detachment stratagems with phase filter</li>
                        <li class="cl-new">Abilities overview panel grouped by phase</li>
                        <li class="cl-new">Detachment rule display in roster header</li>
